title: Tether’s Annual Profit Drops 23% In Midst of Fundraising
description: Tether posted a $10 billion profit in 2025, down 23% from the previous year, as the world’s biggest stablecoin issuer launched a fundraising process that would make it one of the most highly valued private companies.
